{"tid":947517,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙中線紅磡站，首驗3支鋼筋深度，全部不合格","createTime":"2018-12-19T10:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T10:25:07.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"925bb98db8474a3433b809378ee7f95d369f91ea","tid":947517,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=eMUFNY%2B73ln4lj6gV8ZHxRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=063d62b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】港鐵上周開始在沙中線紅磡站擴建工程鑿開石屎檢驗。立法會議員田北辰指，據他收到的消息，第一批檢驗的3支鋼筋，全部扭入螺絲帽的深度均不足。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，原本鋼筋應該扭入40毫米，當中容許3至4毫米偏差，但今次檢驗的3支鋼筋都偏差大約7至10毫米，懷疑都被人剪短。他形容有關不合格比例高得嚇人，難以想像最終結果如何。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E7%AB%99%E9%A6%96%E9%A9%973%E6%94%AF%E9%8B%BC%E7%AD%8B%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6-%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%A0%BC-082941587.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25A3%25A1%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%25A9%25973%25E6%2594%25AF%25E9%258B%25BC%25E7%25AD%258B%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25A0%25BC-082941587.html&d=eMUFNY%2B73ln4lj6gV8ZHxRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=783cee4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E7%AB%99%E9%A6%96%E9%A9%973%E6%94%AF%E9%8B%BC%E7%AD%8B%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6-%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%A0%BC-082941587.html</a>"},{"pid":"9ff32ebf4577938c81e19dc544fcb6c0e682a698","tid":947517,"uid":51021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:25:04.000Z","msg":"Hi Mr Joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0c4add520694e6331cb821bb455fd8086ed784","tid":947517,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018